Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,아빠! 엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,어서 오렴, 카오리
